'''Running Crimson Flightknife''' was a unit of [[Adumari]] [[Blade series]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. Personally commanded by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]], along with his wingman [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]], they led the assault on [[Cartann]] during the [[Adumari Civil War]].

